# Trivy ignore file.
#
# The Azure Storage SDK (@azure/storage-blob) embeds the Azure Storage Emulator's
# well-known, PUBLIC development connection string (account "devstoreaccount1").
# Trivy's secret scanner flags it as an "azure-storage-account-key" CRITICAL, but
# it is a documented public constant, not a leaked secret. Suppress the false
# positive while keeping all real vulnerability and secret scanning.
azure-storage-account-key
